Danet Library (Distributed Asynchronous Network)

=== Compilation ===

Requirements: cmake, g++ (>= 4.7), doxygen

> Configure compilation

 cd build_directory
 cmake source_directory

If you don't want to create documentation automaticly,
you can pass -DMAKE_DOC=OFF option to the cmake command.

> Build Danet

 cd build_directory
 make

You have succefully built Danet library.



=== Build Danet library samples ===

> Compile Danet library (see Compilation)

> Build samples

 cd build_directory
 # Builds chat
 make chat
 # Builds dummy server
 make dyummy-server

You have succefully built Danet library samples
